Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害呢  龍宮小町
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之前才剛剛「決定出道了」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在一下子就忙碌起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡  這還剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓今後能更忙  我還會繼續努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔～真有幹勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得爭取到的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不希望就這麼白白浪費掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要做就要全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律子小姐好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得來幹勁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  製作人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是律子大展身手的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是龍宮小町紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那扇破門修好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:00:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把爛掉的沙發換新
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把電視機換成最新型號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.13,0:01:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想得這麼膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.51,0:01:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要換…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把整個事務所搬到市內一等地區去！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  真是壯觀  律子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  多厲害啊  製作人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺  亞美飛踢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美拳擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓小哥笑得和壞人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓小姐  你的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  剪短了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽說你要剪…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:01:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真虧你能下決心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我覺得這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人站一起時更平衡一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  讓我去剪不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也很喜歡這個造型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為人家說這樣看起來比較年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎  那就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說是高中生也不為過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}高中生有點過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍宮小町計劃也正式開始了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}不不  這是心情上的問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得努力了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================================
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍宮小町是我們765事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上公司命運所打造的偶像組合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請您多多關照了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我就開門見山了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍宮小町是秋月律子製作人的計劃對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  然後成員是  雙海亞美君…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～喜歡的食物是燒雞  佐料汁派
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有水瀨伊織君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和三浦梓君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼選擇這三人的理由是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  平衡比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  平衡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  組合的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為三個人的姓氏都和水有關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以律子取了這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為偶像  還是很在意採訪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我名字裡也有「海」字呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善澤先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來真的是記者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是社長的茶友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是那個嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是龍宮城的公主一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  律子小姐的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…我可是製作人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  美希
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搗亂  沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希能不能也穿上這樣的衣服呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希美希
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會也給亞美戴一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  連亞美也這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}別磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是龍宮城的公主一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到龍宮城就會想到玉手箱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是說不能開就越想打開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  小鳥小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…差不多該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是  碰頭會碰頭會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…不行啊  小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這個時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次採訪可別再說最喜歡燒雞什麼的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:06:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…今天律子她們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是和Amusement  Music的碰頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  能出演那個唱歌節目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是以在那個節目出道為前提的計劃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能出演那個人氣節目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外這週末還有握手會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有唱片店的迷你音樂會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  連一天休息都不剩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得差距很明顯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  765事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}是  總是承蒙您照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須做點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀  這個蛋糕好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了保質期了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶  小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替亞美來陪我玩這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…突然那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家雖然可能已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要以不輸給律子和龍宮小町的氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好帶領大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也請大家一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎麼都沒氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家鼓足幹勁呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是製作人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣毫無方向的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能改變什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想努力  真美我們根本沒工作呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是能有什麼工作的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能像製作人說的那樣努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家想說的我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是由我全力為大家爭取到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765事務所  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔喔喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  製作人先生是不是有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是太累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…幹勁倒是滿滿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜食能讓大腦重新振作起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會會吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  美希
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼美希不是龍宮小町呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個就算你問我也不清楚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是律子…小姐不喜歡美希
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒讓我進龍宮小町吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…應該不是這種理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少美希也應該多表現得認真一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}765事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真的話  美希也能穿上龍宮小町的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能唱能跳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}關於那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  是這邊的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}舞蹈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要努力  大致上…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  應該能跳好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  那美希去努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…啊不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  美希  剛才說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  比起那個  該工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著吧  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  這兩位是我們的新人偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天海春香和菊地真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:10:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是資料…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是如月千早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌非常不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在這裡稍微唱一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…就算在這裡唱也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下  我是765事務所的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩位是我們的新人偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請抽空聽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊織  你伸錯腿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去後再確認一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式演出前一定會練到完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:11:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  現在不辛苦可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  是啊  確實有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  如果是這種內容的話  我覺得彌生應該比我更合適
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  今天還沒看到彌生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  昨天的特攝片跑龍套
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CUT  CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌生有恐高症  受了刺激倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這個工作的話  真或者是我那霸更適合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  雪步她也出問題了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天活動會場來電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太羞人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近製作人該說是有點浮躁呢  還是有點白忙活的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是製作人也是為我們著想才這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  765事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我馬上就去確認  是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不得了了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了  製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動會場聯絡過來問
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你們還有一個偶像沒來  怎麼回事」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得應該是響去這個活動的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  預約重了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響現在和我去別的活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣呢  怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓響繼續做那邊的工作  然後換個人去另一邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  可以讓美希去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  美希嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希  沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拜託了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇啊  美希居然主動要求工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}喂喂  美希說她能去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希  決定要稍微努力一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}好的  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  啊  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  那邊由美希去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人先生  你到那邊去會比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  嗯  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊有春香和我在  沒事的  對吧  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦  製作人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人先生你一個人幹過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了  還有我們在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  請相信我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不好意思  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那邊給我注意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  還有一位馬上就會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  已經太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞蹈的動作  可沒有那麼多時間給她一個人練
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  就算現在來了也沒你的事了  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  給美希看一下舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希看一遍就能記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣跳  然後像這樣後退三步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我把到這裡為止的先重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  請繼續下面的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  剛才這些已經記住了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以請繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  我在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:17:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請相信我們」  嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是765事務所的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次真是太對不起了  全都是我的責任…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫「美希」嗎  她真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  雖然這段時間不太好辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還是想再請你們來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的啊  美希
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看一次動作就記住了  正式表演時也非常好  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希  真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們  幫我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點事  小菜一碟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是  如果要回禮的話  就給美希的工作安排得滿滿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請  喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝了  雪步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  我這裡也有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘鏘  砂糖滿滿的甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  那我就先吃一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  甜死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是甜食補腦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有大家的份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  製作人  昨天辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個  音無小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像最近有些操之過急了  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個甜甜圈  我能吃一個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請介紹一下曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍宮小町  SMOKY  THRILL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊織你咬到舌頭了吧  咬到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚  你真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  節目開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}那麼有請水瀨伊織  三浦梓  雙海亞美組成的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}「龍宮小町」  SMOKY  THRILL  請
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點感動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是才剛剛開始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這不是很完美嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  該說是三人的優點都表現出來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過四人一起敲定的地方也挺多的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會努力不輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.26,0:22:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也必須要學著找出大家的優點  然後發揚光大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起前進吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.15,0:23:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週的偶像大師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是我那霸響哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週巴隆男爵終於要向阿西婭公主告別了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.99,0:24:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇  這是我正在看的輕小說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新說一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.33,0:24:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好期待
